CIA Triad
Confidentiality: Who is allowed to access
Integrity: Prove the authenticity of data
Availability: Readiness 

AAA
Authentication: Proving one’s identity
Authorization: Which access is allowed
Accounting: Logs
Gap Analysis - Where we are vs Where we want to be 
Zero Trust - MFA, Least Priv. 
Block Chain - Common Ledger, hashing of transactions, sharing the transactions & ledger with all users
Certificates - CA Authority, Certificate Revocation List (CRL)
Threat Actors - Unskilled, Hacktivists, Nation States, Organized Crime, Shadow IT, Insider 
Threat Vector - method used by attacker to access your system 
